# Category C: Federated DP Training with HUKLLA-Halt
# Upstream: adap/flower (Apache-2.0) commit fd50dd0eed8f
#           pytorch/opacus (Apache-2.0) commit 88919b6677bb
# Fashion: HUKLLA-halt when cumulative DP epsilon exceeds DPI_CAP
